{"tid":851434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港13歲女CEO葉礽僖 香港電台訪問","createTime":"2018-10-07T06:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:33:34.000Z","uid":1772,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c266c177a14c4b2248dd6590b3dcbef5c2a43e19","tid":851434,"uid":1772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zNFnlTuzTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9zNFnlTuzTA&d=MCz2kgrv25DYtuinWPPTItibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=cf30be8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zNFnlTuzTA</a><br />\n睇佢present果陣好流利同埋幾有信心，值得欣賞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且咁細年紀諗野已經咁成熟，無可否認真係幾出色<br />\n<br />\n不過感覺上同人相處好似麻麻地，條片 <ins>9:57</ins> 開始講佢同佢細佬相處<br />\n佢細佬直情爆粗鬧佢「死仆街」<br />\n當佢阿媽鬧佢細路時 個女仔仲陰陰咀笑咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住獨立訪問細佬時又係咁數臭家姐<br />\n<br />\nBTW 唔知佢真正參與幾多研發同埋屋企人幫左幾多手<br />\n無証無據 唔想亂咁係哩方面評論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6ObJX-OGrg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW6ObJX-OGrg&d=MCz2kgrv25DYtuinWPPTItibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=921a6e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W6ObJX-OGrg</a><br />\n睇完條片之後去左搵佢研發嘅App<br />\n首先讚下個UI UX做得唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但發覺D功能好似幾怪獸家長<br />\n有個家長監控功能可以ban自己仔女同咩細路傾計<br />\n同埋幫自己仔女過濾男性/女性或者年齡朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪真係有需要呢"},{"pid":"229437c17fb440638f464fa43ce0cc6a979d4354","tid":851434,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:58:25.000Z","msg":"binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41c4d68d5984687aa42293a441462281c4b0415","tid":851434,"uid":146055,"like":